This is ball collision simulator using python

User can add or remove ball with left mouse click

You should also check video from Coding train I took idea from: https://youtu.be/dJNFPv9Mj-Y?si=J24Hl7LnQdwtVnps

Wikipedia article about phisics I used to create this: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Elastic_collision#Two-dimensional